author: zairahira
message: fix(curriculum): update test 14 Travel Agency Lab (#57620)

files.patch:
@@ -100,8 +100,7 @@ You should have a `p` element below the `h1` element.
 
 ```js
 assert.strictEqual(
-  document.querySelector('h1')?.nextElementSibling,
-  document.querySelector('p')
+  document.querySelector('h1')?.nextElementSibling.tagName, 'P'
 );
 ```
 
@@ -121,8 +120,7 @@ You should have a `p` element below your first `h2` element.
 
 ```js
 assert.strictEqual(
-  document.querySelector('h2')?.nextElementSibling,
-  document.querySelectorAll('p')?.[1]
+    document.querySelector('h2')?.nextElementSibling.tagName, 'P'
 );
 ```
